{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_07_04",
  "title": "LizNoir 07 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……あの二人はこれまでも遠慮なくぶつかってきた\nそれが出来るのは強い信頼関係があるからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Those two have clashed without holding back before\nThe reason they can do that is because they have a strong trusting relationship",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.7578912735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも葵も、LizNoirを大切に思ってる\nもう少しだけ、愛とこころも二人を見守ってみないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both Rio-san and Aoi cherish LizNoir\nSo‚ for a little while longer‚ why don't we‚ Ai and Kokoro‚ watch over them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9999999682,
      "endTime": 16.486258284199998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "でも……今回のケンカは\n今までとは違うような気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… this fight\nI feel like it's different from before",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6999999682,
      "endTime": 22.550362555099998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あの～……。BIG4という目標に突き進む莉央さんと\nリズノワらしさを大事にしたい葵さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey~…. With Rio-san who is pushing forward towards the goal of BIG4\nand Aoi-san who wants to cherish LizNoir's identity…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7666666348,
      "endTime": 31.8321991284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "どっちが正しいと思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who do you think is right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0333333015,
      "endTime": 34.409909296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルである以上、トップを目指すのは当然だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As long as they are idols‚ it's natural for them to aim for the top",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5999999682,
      "endTime": 38.073786846800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、{user}さんは\n莉央さんが正しいと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ {user}-san\nyou think Rio-san is right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2666666348,
      "endTime": 42.168256076199995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、葵のこだわりも正しいと思う\nそれがLizNoirをここまで押し上げてきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I think Aoi's stubbornness is also right\nThat's what has pushed LizNoir this far",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3666686694,
      "endTime": 48.8273489634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ全然答えになってません\nこころ達は、どうすればいいんですか～っ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not an answer at all\nWhat should we do~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.033335336,
      "endTime": 54.9910902341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ぶつかり合わなきゃ見つからない答えがある\n今はその時だと俺は思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are answers that can only be found by clashing with each other\nI think now is that time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2000020027,
      "endTime": 60.8852520943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もう少しだけ待ってみないか？\nもし助けが必要な時がきたら、その時は俺達の出番だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ why don't we wait a little longer?\nIf a time comes when they need help‚ that's when it's our turn",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2999989509,
      "endTime": 69.8465309142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.08333381
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.08333381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの言うことは分かるけど……\n何もしないで見守るのって難しいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand what {user}-san is saying‚ but……\nIt's difficult to just watch and do nothing‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.13333381,
      "endTime": 79.09752887069999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.3000004767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……それじゃあ、愛\n二人の仲直り、私達が手伝ってみない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In that case‚ Ai\nWhy don't we help them‚ make up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3000004767,
      "endTime": 85.521678543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.73333381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも\n{user}さんはまだその時じゃないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But\n{user}-san said it's not the time yet",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.73333381,
      "endTime": 90.75955823250001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.9666559536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが言ってたでしょー？\n「見守ってみないか」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san said it‚ didn't heー?\nWhy don't we watch over them?'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9666559536,
      "endTime": 95.18720010109999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.399989287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "それって、見守る分には何をしても構わないって\nことだよね？　だったら二人にくっついてみようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That means we can do whatever we want as long as we're watching over them‚\nright? Then let's stick close to them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.399989287,
      "endTime": 103.1111473718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "そして今の想いを聞き出して、もう片方に伝えるの\n最近二人とも顔を合わせても全然喋ってないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then we'll find out what they're thinking and tell the other person\nThey haven't been talking at all even when they meet each other recently……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3333236376,
      "endTime": 112.8874959628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 108.3666676838
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.0999903042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね……今の先輩達は気持ちを素直に\n伝え合うことさえ難しそうだもんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right…… It seems difficult for our senpai\nto be honest with their feelings right now……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0999903042,
      "endTime": 121.4678814251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.6666569709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "何もしないよりはずっといい。やろう、こころ\nでも『脱退』とか『解散』とか危険ワードが出たら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's much better than doing nothing. Let's do it‚ Kokoro\nBut if dangerous words like \"withdrawal\" or \"disbandment\" come out……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6666569709,
      "endTime": 129.8666661579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.8999821662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、その時はすぐ{user}さんに報告だよ\n報・連・相は社会人のキホン？　だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-Then‚ we'll report it to {user}-san right away\nReporting‚ communicating‚ and consulting are the basics for an adult‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8999821662,
      "endTime": 137.4534516334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.6666488329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、ここからは別行動ってことで！\n私は莉央さんをマークするから、愛は葵さんをお願い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ from here on out‚ let's work separately!\nI'll take care of Rio-san‚ and Ai will take care of Aoi-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6666488329,
      "endTime": 144.4370076815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、分かった！　連絡はこまめにとろうね\n何かあったらお互いすぐに駆けつけられるようにしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ got it! We keep in touch often\nLet's be ready to run to each other's side if something happens",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6333114306,
      "endTime": 152.2277807871,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 23133.36184810001,
          "startTime": 167.7666732787
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 153.6978403728
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.0166539191
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.0166539191
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "…………体が重いし、調子が戻らない\nこれじゃ、莉央に偉そうなこと、言えないな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…My body is heavy‚ and I can't get back into condition\nI can't say anything so proudly to Rio if I'm like this……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0666539191,
      "endTime": 168.153207302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.3666539191
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、葵さん\n随分ハードな練習をされていたみたいですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your effort‚ Aoi-san\nIt seems like you've been practicing very hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3666539191,
      "endTime": 174.3199942587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.5333277065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "君か……。なんだかよく会うね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's you…… We meet often‚ don't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.5333277065,
      "endTime": 178.7173413593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran002.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、決勝トーナメントに参加することを\n決められたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you perhaps decide to participate in the final tournament?\nin the final tournament?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9333277065,
      "endTime": 183.6133368809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.8000035285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……そういう訳じゃないけど\n踊っていないと落ち着かなくて。出来は最悪だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's not it‚ but\nI feel anxious when I stop dancing. The performance is terrible‚ though",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8000035285,
      "endTime": 190.9935200691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないです！　とても素敵なパフォーマンス\nでした！　葵さんはご自分に厳し過ぎます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true! It was a very wonderful performance\nthat you gave! Aoi-san is too hard on yourself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.200005563,
      "endTime": 200.1333340008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.3333338101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、なんだか後輩達みたいなことを言うね\nどうして君は僕のことをそんなに気にするの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you're saying things like my kohai\nWhy do you care about me so much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.3333338101,
      "endTime": 208.3229481061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.5666742642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran004.m4a",
      "text": "……それは、葵さんが、私の姉に似ているからです\nだから……なんだか他人だとは思えなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's because‚ Aoi-san‚ you're similar to my older sister\nSo…… I don't feel like you someone else……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.5666742642,
      "endTime": 219.95999320340002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 220.1666600227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、お姉さんがいるんだ。どんな人なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehー‚ you have an older sister. What kind of person is she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.1666600227,
      "endTime": 224.1634626388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran005.m4a",
      "text": "……もう亡くなっているんです。姉も葵さんみたいに\n凄くまっすぐで自分のパフォーマンスに厳しい人でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…She's already gone. My sister‚ just like Aoi-san‚\nwas a very straightforward person who was strict about her own performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.3666600227,
      "endTime": 234.3199946404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran006.m4a",
      "text": "だからでしょうか。葵さんに姉を重ねてしまい……\nもっと沢山話しておけば良かったって……後悔していて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that's why. I can't help but see my sister in you‚ Aoi-san…\nI regret that I didn't talk to her more… so I'm sorry for being pushy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.7333246548,
      "endTime": 246.51998751949998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.9999984422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran007.m4a",
      "text": "しつこくしてしまって、すみませんでした。でも……\nもし悩み事があるなら、私で良ければ聞かせて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for being so persistent. But……\nIf you have any worries‚ I'll listen if it's okay with you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.9999984422,
      "endTime": 257.393335978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 257.6000025111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……まいったな。そこまで言われちゃうと、僕も話す\nしかないじゃないか。自分語りは苦手なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You've got me there. If you say that much‚ I have no choice but to talk\nI'm not good at talking about myself",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.6000025111,
      "endTime": 267.25659278210003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 267.4666610398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……迷ってるんだ。自分達らしさや誇り……\n大切なものを捨ててまで、頂点を目指すべきなのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm conflicted. Our identity and pride……\nshould we aim for the top even if it means throwing away something important?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.4666610398,
      "endTime": 278.4400848069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 278.6333277064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央はそうすべきだって言う。理屈は分かる\n莉央がどんな気持ちでそう言っているのかも、分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio says we should. I understand the why\nI also understand how she feels when she says that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.6333277064,
      "endTime": 288.304574998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 288.4999943731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "でも……それが正しいとは\n僕にはどうしても思えないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…… I can't aceept it\nI can't bring myself to believe that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.4999943731,
      "endTime": 294.0718602178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "大切なものを捨ててまで得たトップの座なんかに\n意味なんてあるのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there any meaning in reaching the top\nif it's by giving up something important?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.3999760625,
      "endTime": 299.618411636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 299.9999658899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことを考えていたら僕の手が、足が重たくなって\n――気付けば、今までみたいに踊れなくなってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about that made my hands and feet feel heavy\n――Before I knew it‚ I couldn't dance like I used to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.9999658899,
      "endTime": 310.3704195337,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10800.038687599965,
          "startTime": 310.8000045775
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 310.7333195683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "葵さ～ん……あれ？　誰かとお話し中だ\nあの人確か決勝トーナメントに出場する『綺羅』の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san~…… Huh? She's talking to someone\nThat person… I think she's from \"Kira\"‚ who's in the final tournament……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.7333195683,
      "endTime": 321.0458155629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 321.2333216028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran008.m4a",
      "text": "……お話してくれてありがとうございます\n私は……莉央さんの方針に問題があると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you for listening to me\nI…… I think there's a problem with Rio-san's policy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 321.2333216028,
      "endTime": 330.63999055190004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央は悪くないよ\nでも、君はどうしてそう思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rio is not at fault\nBut‚ why do you think that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.8333236374,
      "endTime": 335.9960674919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 336.199990304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran009.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんの自由を奪ってパフォーマンスの質を落としたら\nリズノワにとっては本末転倒です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you take away Aoi-san's freedom and lower the quality of the performance\nit would be a total loss for LizNoir",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.199990304,
      "endTime": 343.9333031969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-ranran010.m4a",
      "text": "今のリズノワ……いえ、莉央さんはBIG4に固執する\nあまり、葵さんを大切にしていないように感じます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The current LizNoir…… no‚ Rio-san is obsessed with BIG4\nI feel like she doesn't value Aoi-san very much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 344.1333032923,
      "endTime": 353.55329745589995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 353.7666305222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_04-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "…………そっか。じゃあ僕はそろそろ練習に戻るよ\n話を聞いてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. Well‚ I'm going back to practice now\nThank you for listening",
